title: Children’s charities benefit from Murdoch’s cinema partnership (Murdoch University)
text: ( Source : Murdoch University ) Murdoch University helped to raise more than $800, 000 for children's charities thanks to its partnership with McDonald's Community Cinemas in 2014/15. Ten local charities each received proceeds from the 14th
